"1  medium jicama (about 1 pound)","3  navel oranges, peeled, halved lengthwise, and cut crosswise into 1/4-inch-thick slices (about 1 1/2 cups)","2  small cucumbers, peeled, halved lengthwise, seeded, and thinly sliced (about 3 cups)","1/2 cup thinly sliced radishes","1/3 cup fresh lime juice","2 teaspoons dried ground guajillo chile or hot chili powder","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/3 cup coarsely chopped fresh cilantro"